u1ebfn Chelsea cay c\u00fa</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5539","checkdouble":"194580"},{"date":"08:03 16/08","title":"Gerrard tham v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m HLV\u2026 Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/4/gerrard-tham-vong-duoc-lam-hlv-man-utd.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alex Miller nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Liverpool, Arsenal hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Manchester United m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u00e1m d\u1ed7 l\u00f4i k\u00e9o Steven Gerrard ra kh\u1ecfi gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng HLV c\u1ee7a Rangers.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y, Steven Gerrard \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang m\u1ed9t trang m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Sau khi treo gi\u00e0y gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 38 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c HLV \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i U18 c\u1ee7a Liverpool, m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 x\u01b0a \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gerrard l\u00e0m HLV Rangers tham v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gerrard l\u00e0m HLV Rangers tham v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/4/gerrard-tham-vong-duoc-lam-hlv-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gerrard l\u00e0m HLV Rangers</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 nhanh ch\u00f3ng, Gerrard ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn khi nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Rangers c\u1ee7a Scotland. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi ng\u1ed3i l\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng s\u00e2n Ibrox, bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a The Kop \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ea3 trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Gerrard ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 38 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Anh \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u1ed9t CLB Premier League nh\u01b0ng theo Alex Miller, \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u00e1m d\u1ed7 l\u00f4i k\u00e9o anh ra kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u HLV t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eadp ni\u00ean l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Anfield \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2008: \u201cM\u1ed9t khi anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u1edf Rangers th\u00ec anh c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u c\u01a1 ch\u1ee9? \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 Liverpool, Arsenal hay Manchester United m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u201d \u2013 Gerrard s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1eddi chung trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Rangers \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t Scotland sau th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i l\u1eadn \u0111\u1eadn \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ecb gi\u00e1ng xu\u1ed1ng do ch\u00ecm trong n\u1ee3 n\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Gerrard v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi Celtic c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Brendan Rodgers.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5538","checkdouble":"194569"},{"date":"00:22 16/08","title":"Luke Shaw b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3m b\u00e9o","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/luke-shaw-bat-dau-chien-dich-giam-beo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Luke Shaw \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf r\u1eb1ng anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3m b\u00e9o sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i v\u00ec d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. B\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i v\u00f3c d\u00e1ng l\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi chuy\u00ean gia dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, ki\u00eam \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ebfp Jonny Marsh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Manchester United t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9, Shaw \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m v\u00ec th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh to l\u1edbn, kh\u1eafc h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh anh khi m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford. Nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u00e9o ph\u00ec sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i b\u1ecb Jose Mourinho \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Shaw \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean gia c\u1ee7a sao Man City, Luke Shaw gi\u1ea3m b\u00e9o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean gia c\u1ee7a sao Man City, Luke Shaw gi\u1ea3m b\u00e9o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/luke-shaw-noi-gi-sau-khi-ghi-ban-thang-dau-tien-cho-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Leicester City l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Shaw.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City, Luke Shaw \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i v\u00f3c d\u00e1ng, phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Marsh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap anh gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng ng\u1ee7 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nShaw ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Marsh t\u1ea1i Anh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ebfp n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kevin de Bruyne, Kyle Walker, Ilkay Gundogan, Maroane Fellaini v\u00e0 John Terry thu\u00ea l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Theo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Marsh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn nh\u00e0 Luke Shaw \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1ea5u b\u1eefa t\u1ed1i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Ngo\u00e0i ra trong nh\u1eefng n\u00e0y Shaw ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Marsh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1eefa \u0103n nh\u1eb9, \u0111\u1ed3 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay Shaw kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t, Jose Mourinho s\u1ebd c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 12 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5537","checkdouble":"194573"},{"date":"19:15 15/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 15/8: V\u00ec Man Utd, Zidane s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eadt k\u00e8o Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-158-vi-man-utd-zidane-san-sang-lat-keo-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 15/8.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zidane nh\u1eafm gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Man Utd</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 158 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 158 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/ngay-hom-nay-18.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Zinedine Zidane</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia tay Real Madrid tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh vinh quang, Zidane c\u0169ng s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u1ee5 Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m \u1edf Juventus. Tuy nhi\u00ean, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eadt k\u00e8o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Man Utd v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m sau. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng HLV c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho \u0111ang lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i \u1edf Old Trafford b\u1edfi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sarri ghi th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ed9ng \u1edf Chelsea<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 158 V\u00ec Man Utd, Zidane s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eadt k\u00e8o Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 158 V\u00ec Man Utd, Zidane s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eadt k\u00e8o Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-158-Vi-Man-Utd,-Zidane-san-sang-lat-keo-Juventus-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Maurizio Sarri</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi th\u1ed5i v\u00e0o Stamford Bridge, Maurizio Sarri d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi \u1edf Chelsea, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t so v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Antonio Conte. Theo \u0111\u00f3, t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1edbi l\u1ecfng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 \u00edt kh\u1eaft khe h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f3i quen tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn MU \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean v\u00ec Pogba <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba vo dich the gioi\" title=\"Pogba v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/chu-tich-barca-chua-tu-bo-y-dinh-cuom-pogba-khoi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Paul Pogba</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tranh th\u1ee7 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p gi\u1eefa Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Jose Mourinho c\u00f9ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n chia tay Man Utd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, Barcelona l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y. Sau ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Josep Maria Bartomeu th\u00ec G\u0110TT Ariedo Braida c\u0169ng \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cu\u1ed7m ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t Old Trafford v\u1ec1 Camp Nou, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 danh t\u00ednh nh\u1eb1m t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u00e1c CLB kh\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chia tay ng\u00f4i sao ti\u1ebfp theo<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Drinkwater\" title=\"Drinkwater\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/26/drinkwater-vua-mac-phai-sai-lam-lon-nhat-doi-minh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Danny Drinkwater</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e8 l\u00e0 Jorginho, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 k\u00e9o theo, t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u1ecdn d\u1eb9p thanh l\u00fd trong th\u00e1ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y. Sau khi Tiemoue Bakayoko \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Milan, Danny Drinkwater c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo ph\u1ea3i chia tay Chelsea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sao Man Utd cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Old Trafford<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Herrera\" title=\"Herrera\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ander Herrera</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng Ander Herrera c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u00edt lo l\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i \u1edf. T\u00ecnh y\u00eau Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 x\u1ee9 Basque l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i v\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 d\u00e0i l\u00e2u v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Chuy\u1ec7n gia h\u1ea1n d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV v\u00e0 BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sao Liverpool chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Napoli<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Mignolet\" title=\"thu mon Mignolet\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/20/Vuot-mat-Barca,-Napoli-muon-mua-Simon-Mignolet-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Simon Mignolet</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 Alisson Becker v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Loris Karius c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng h\u01a1n cho vai tr\u00f2 k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong khung g\u1ed7 Anfield cho Simon Mignolet g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, thay v\u00ec b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 danh gi\u00e1 Barcelona th\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Napoli n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef v\u1ec1 m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"San moi cua Tottenham dang trong qua trinh hoan thien va du kien mo cua vao ngay 15/9.\" title=\"S\u00e2n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn m\u1edf c\u1eeda v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 15/9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-he-2018-Mua-khong-noi,-ban-chang-xong!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>S\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Tottenham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Tottenham d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng Ch\u00edn t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ngay trong m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u00ec m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do hay s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 ngo\u00e0i \u00fd mu\u1ed1n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n l\u1ea1i v\u00f4 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t cho t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng M\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ed9t. Trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y, Spurs s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Wembley l\u00e0m s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5536","checkdouble":"194555"}]}